//Needs Review 

## **üéØ Learning Preferences** (Major Missing Category)

### **Hint System Settings**
- **Hint Behavior**: Auto-show vs. click-to-reveal
- **Hint Penalties**: Enable/disable point deductions
- **Progressive Hints**: Show all levels vs. one at a time
- **Hint Timing**: Delay before hints become available (0-30 seconds)
- **Independence Goals**: Target % of exercises completed without hints

### **Difficulty & Progression**
- **Auto-Difficulty Adjustment**: Enable adaptive difficulty based on performance
- **Starting Difficulty Level**: 1-9 scale for new content
- **Progression Speed**: Conservative, Normal, Aggressive
- **Grammar Focus Areas**: Prioritize specific concepts (verb tenses, gender, etc.)
- **Mistake Tolerance**: How many errors before content difficulty decreases

### **Grading System Preferences**
- **Scoring Strictness**: Lenient, Standard, Strict
- **Grade Display**: Show letter grades, percentages, or both
- **Performance Tracking**: Enable detailed analytics vs. simple progress

## **üîä Audio & Voice Settings** (Critical for Language Learning)

### **Text-to-Speech**
- **Voice Gender**: Male, Female, or Mixed
- **Speech Speed**: 0.5x to 2.0x playback speed
- **Regional Accent**: Match location setting (Mexican, Argentine, etc.)
- **Auto-Pronunciation**: Read sentences aloud automatically
- **Voice Quality**: Standard vs. Premium voices

### **Voice Recognition** (Future Feature)
- **Microphone Sensitivity**: For pronunciation practice
- **Accent Training**: Enable pronunciation feedback
- **Voice Commands**: Navigate app with voice

## **üé® Interface & Display Settings**

### **Visual Preferences**
- **Theme Options**: Dark (current), Light, Auto-switch by time
- **Color Scheme**: Strike (current), High Contrast, Colorblind-friendly
- **Font Size**: Small, Medium, Large, Extra Large
- **Animation Speed**: Fast, Normal, Slow, Disabled
- **Reduced Motion**: For accessibility

### **Layout Options**
- **Sidebar Behavior**: Always visible, Auto-hide, Manual toggle
- **Compact Mode**: Reduce spacing for smaller screens
- **Progress Indicators**: Show/hide various progress elements

## **üìö Content & Reading Settings**

### **Content Preferences**
- **Content Types**: Prioritize books, news, conversations, AI stories
- **Content Sources**: Enable/disable specific content providers
- **Reading Goals**: Pages per day, minutes per session
- **Complexity Preference**: Gradually increase vs. mixed difficulty

### **Reading Interface**
- **Word Highlighting**: Color-code by difficulty
- **Click Behavior**: Instant translation vs. hover preview
- **Context Display**: Show word usage examples
- **Reading Speed Tracking**: Enable WPM calculations

## **üß† Memory & Flash Card Settings**

### **Spaced Repetition**
- **Algorithm Type**: Standard SM-2, Modified, or Custom intervals
- **Review Frequency**: Daily, Every 2 days, Weekly
- **Session Size**: Max cards per review session (10-50)
- **Difficulty Adjustment**: Manual vs. automatic card difficulty

### **Flash Card Display**
- **Card Animation**: Flip speed and style
- **Answer Buttons**: 2-button (Again/Good) vs. 4-button system
- **Context Display**: Always show original sentence vs. on-demand
- **Progress Indicators**: Show mastery level on cards

## **üí¨ Conversation Settings**

### **AI Chat Preferences**
- **Default Persona**: Casual, Formal, Teacher, Native Speaker
- **Correction Frequency**: Every mistake, Major errors only, End of conversation
- **Vocabulary Complexity**: Introduce new words vs. stick to known vocabulary
- **Conversation Length**: Short (5-10 exchanges), Medium, Long sessions
- **Topic Preferences**: Rank favorite conversation topics

### **Learning Integration**
- **Auto-Add Vocabulary**: Automatically bookmark new words from conversations
- **Grammar Feedback**: Real-time vs. end-of-conversation
- **Cultural Context**: Include cultural explanations and references

## **üîê Privacy & Data Management**

### **Data Control**
- **Data Export**: Download all learning data (JSON, CSV)
- **Data Import**: Import progress from other apps
- **Account Deletion**: Full account removal with data cleanup
- **Learning History**: Retention period (1 year, 2 years, Forever)

### **Analytics & Tracking**
- **Usage Analytics**: Opt-in/out of anonymous usage tracking
- **Performance Data**: Share learning data for app improvement
- **Third-Party Integrations**: Connect with other learning platforms

## **üì± Mobile & Sync Settings**

### **Offline Mode**
- **Content Download**: Download content for offline practice
- **Sync Frequency**: Real-time, WiFi only, Manual
- **Storage Management**: Auto-delete old content
- **Background Sync**: Update progress when app is closed

### **Device Settings**
- **Multi-Device Sync**: Sync progress across devices
- **Backup Settings**: Automatic cloud backup
- **Cache Management**: Clear cache, cache size limits

## **üîî Enhanced Notification Settings**

### **Learning Reminders**
- **Daily Practice**: Customize time and frequency
- **Review Reminders**: Flash card review notifications
- **Streak Alerts**: Warn before streak breaks
- **Achievement Notifications**: Celebrate milestones

### **Progress Updates**
- **Weekly Summary**: Progress report emails
- **Goal Reminders**: Practice target notifications
- **Motivation Messages**: Encouraging push notifications
- **Social Sharing**: Auto-share achievements (optional)

## **üõ†Ô∏è Advanced & Debug Settings**

### **Developer Options** (Hidden by default)
- **API Response Times**: Show performance metrics
- **Cache Statistics**: View cache hit rates
- **Debug Mode**: Enable detailed error logging
- **Beta Features**: Access experimental features
- **Reset Options**: Reset specific data types

### **Accessibility**
- **Screen Reader Support**: Enhanced compatibility
- **Keyboard Navigation**: Full keyboard app control
- **High Contrast**: Enhanced visual accessibility
- **Motion Sensitivity**: Reduce animations for sensitive users

## **üìä Goal & Target Settings**

### **Enhanced Practice Targets**
- **Daily Goals**: Sentences, words, minutes
- **Weekly Challenges**: Cross-page activity goals
- **Monthly Milestones**: Long-term learning objectives
- **Adaptive Goals**: Adjust targets based on performance
- **Goal Reminders**: Notification timing and frequency

## **üìã Settings Page Organization**

```typescript
interface SettingsStructure {
  "Learning": {
    "Hint System": HintSettings,
    "Difficulty & Progression": DifficultySettings,
    "Goals & Targets": TargetSettings
  },
  "App Preferences": {
    "Language & Region": LanguageSettings,
    "Audio & Voice": AudioSettings,
    "Interface & Display": InterfaceSettings
  },
  "Content Settings": {
    "Reading Preferences": ReadingSettings,
    "Flash Cards": FlashCardSettings,
    "Conversations": ConversationSettings
  },
  "Account & Privacy": {
    "User Profile": UserSettings,
    "Privacy & Data": PrivacySettings,
    "Security": SecuritySettings
  },
  "Device & Sync": {
    "Notifications": NotificationSettings,
    "Offline & Sync": SyncSettings,
    "Advanced": AdvancedSettings
  }
}
```

This comprehensive settings system gives users **complete control** over their Spanish learning experience while maintaining the clean, organized interface your app is known for! üéõÔ∏è